  "elapsed_s": 189.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And-- and of course, if you have to go, you have to go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And every time you had to go, of course, it-- when the bucket was filled up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "It-- it-- it's a little humor in here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "When the bucket was filled up, of course the last guy doing it had to carry it out and they would take down his number to make sure that he comes back.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "So nobody-- everybody was afraid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So everybody was just waiting for the guy to take it out and then suddenly, bingo, in the next five minutes, the bucket is full again and somebody has to go and pick it up.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were all having fun with it at night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, sitting around or waiting in your-- in your bunk bed until somebody took it out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every time you left the barracks, if you had to go really-- if you have to go to the toilet for a bowel movement or so, they would, of course, write down your number you could go-- undressed, of course, going in there.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, we will get a-- a-- This is the end of tape number two.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
